node.text:
@EmilHartoonian offering this $9,950,000 home in Pacific Palisades - 909 Greentree Rd - This brand-new retreat offers exquisite design, an ideal location, and an ultra-private lifestyle of leisure in the Rustic Canyon community. With 7 bedrooms, 9 baths, and 8,683 square feet across 3 levels, the home boasts glistening stone and brass elements, an outdoor haven, and spectacular amenities. Pristine landscaping leads to the entrance where residents are greeted by hardwood floors and 11-foot ceilings.

Contact @EmilHartoonian for more information
